            <title>[CASSANDRA-2270] nodetool info NPE when node isn&apos;t fully booted</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-2270</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
