                            <comment id="13002640" author="jbellis" created="Fri, 4 Mar 2011 14:57:56 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;By &quot;not yet ready&quot; do you mean early in normal startup, or started up with explicitly not joining ring?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13002642" author="wajam" created="Fri, 4 Mar 2011 15:01:17 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Early in normal startup, just run &quot;nodetool -h localhost info&quot; when the node its still opening index.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
